===============================================================================
= Package Name: polar2grid
= Author:       David Hoese, Ray Garcia, Eva Schiffer, William Straka (SSEC)
= Organization: Space Science and Engineering Center (SSEC UW-Madison)
= Description:  Library and scripts for remapping VIIRS data to AWIPS NC files
===============================================================================

Installation
============
polar2grid should be used as an internal package to the polar2grid Workspace.
The Workspace includes C, IDL, and Python programs/libraries to properly go
from VIIRS data to AWIPS NC file.

